anced by its use as a British royal name for  Prince Andrew  (  b. 1960 ), the Duke of York."],"variants":[]},{"name":"Arnot","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["originally a short form of names beginning with <i>arn</i> ‘eagle’, for example   Arnold   and   Arnulf ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Andrew Arnot Cameron Laird was born in 1400, in Portmoak, Kinross-shire, Scotland, United Kingdom. He had at least 2 daughters. He died in 1440, in Argyll, Scotland, United Kingdom, at the age of 40."},"et":{"1400–1440":"1400–1440","1430–1460":"1430–1460","1433–1460":"1433–1460","1400":"1400","1433":"1433","1430":"1430","1440":"1440","1460":"1460","Portmoak, Kinross-shire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Portmoak, Kinross-shire, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Lochowe, Argyll, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Argyll, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1400–1440":"1400–1440","1430–1460":"1430–1460","1433–1460":"1433–1460","1400":"1400","1433":"1433","1430":"1430","1440":"1440","1460":"1460","Portmoak, Kinross-shire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Portmoak, Kinross-shire, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Lochowe, Argyll, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Argyll, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1400–1440":"1400–1440","1430–1460":"1430–1460","1433–1460":"1433–1460","1400":"1400","1433":"1433","1430":"1430","1440":"1440","1460":"1460","Portmoak, Kinross-shire, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Portmoak, Kinross-shire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","Lochowe, Argyll, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Argyll, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Andrew Arnot Cameron Laird est né en 1400, à Portmoak, Kinross-shire, Écosse, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 2 filles. Il est décédé en 1440, à Argyll, Écosse, Royaume-Uni, à l’âge de 40 ans."},"de":{"1400–1440":"1400–1440","1430–1460":"1430–1460","1433–1460":"1433–1460","1400":"1400","1433":"1433","1430":"1430","1440":"1440","1460":"1460","Portmoak, Kinross-shire, Scotland, United Kingdom